    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苍蝇骑士》讲述了一名苍蝇骑士团侍从的故事。在游戏中，你将扮演这位侍从。在骑士团的召集下，你参与了对女巫月蛾的讨伐，试图解除那个让大家无法长出翅膀的诅咒。在一次埋伏后，你与队伍失散，独自来到了沼泽居民的村庄，并发誓要完成这项任务——无论是孤身奋战，还是与沿途中召唤而来的战士并肩作战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否有能力克服各种挑战，赢得真正的骑士称号？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/5bb0eee7444e9353dd96ca6272aa0f2c.poster.avif?t=1761565657\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/5bb0eee7444e9353dd96ca6272aa0f2c.webm?t=1761565657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用各种武器武装自己，选择最适合当前状况的武器：砍断敌人的手臂可以断其攻势；击碎敌人的头颅可以使其失去知觉；使用长武器或弓箭可以拉开战斗距离。巧妙应对每一场战斗来取得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/4f79fe5ac27c9ec979768641f0eab89a.poster.avif?t=1761565657\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/4f79fe5ac27c9ec979768641f0eab89a.webm?t=1761565657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精心打造的关卡世界，每一条岔路都藏着宝物和杀机。努力抵达下一个存档点，对抗一心想置你于死地的强大头目，证明你的实力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/a5b4a5ef51c68df646d333460cc913d1.poster.avif?t=1761565657\" width=600 height=121 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/a5b4a5ef51c68df646d333460cc913d1.webm?t=1761565657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤朋友一起探索月蛾巢穴：兵分两路，互相协作，交换物品，还能做出各种动作互动。游戏支持2到4人联机，能够保存所有人的进度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/8b0c521afcd527cbb5b309798e8fa0c1.poster.avif?t=1761565657\" width=600 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/8b0c521afcd527cbb5b309798e8fa0c1.webm?t=1761565657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以拿出钓鱼竿，在存档点稍作休息。钓上一袋子营养丰富的奇特生物，如果使用得当，它们会给你带来增益效果和战斗优势……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/aa65de33af3c31066c10407dbf6a1d17.poster.avif?t=1761565657\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108510/extras/aa65de33af3c31066c10407dbf6a1d17.webm?t=1761565657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索迷宫会让你获得丰厚的奖励，你可以根据自己的喜好自定义装备，打造属于你的角色。</p>",
